{"tid":2038223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[全世界散出去] 2021﹐中共沒日","createTime":"2020-05-27T12:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T12:24:30.000Z","uid":38929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb00c8e9c2ce854a04407178cbf901105efd9d4","tid":2038223,"uid":38929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴絲打，有無發現〔<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">天滅中共</span></span></strong>〕這句，唔係唔好，但係  ...... <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">無一個期限！！</span></span><br />\n天係會滅佢，但幾時？！<br />\n<br />\n一個月？兩個月？半年？一年？十年？<br />\n<br />\n你地等得，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班水深火熱手足唔等得！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁，點解唔俾個期限佢？<br />\n以現在局勢來看，2020內應該做唔到，但2021呢，應該就係個時機！！<br />\n我想要一句新口號<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2021﹐中共沒日</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁多次改朝換代，都一定有一些什麼童謠、順口溜之類，於民間流傳，使人民相信，天數已定，暴政必亡，我地一齊讓這句成為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">覆滅中共</span></span></span></strong>的天數，更要它成為事實！<br />\n<br />\n中共滅亡，香港才有救！"}]}